ngram\": \"their berths\", \"from\": 284, \"to\": 296}, {\"ngram\": \"this summer's showpiece\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there was heartbreak for super heavyweight Galway boxer, Martin McDonagh, who was unable to make it a clean sweep for the Irish quintet in Sunday's Olympic deciders.\", \"from\": 326, \"to\": 495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 373, \"end\": 379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Galway_GAA\", \"score\": 0.9999999998426574, \"rank\": 1.4378371305715473e-10, \"text\": \"Galway\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Galway_GAA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Galway_GAA\"}, {\"begin\": 387, \"end\": 402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_McDonagh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Martin McDonagh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_McDonagh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_McDonagh\"}, {\"begin\": 452, \"end\": 457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999152644054777, \"rank\": 7.692630414298307e-05, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sunday's Olympic deciders\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McDonagh was beaten by the narrowest of margins, going down to Armenia's Davit Chaloyan on a 3:2 split decision.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 497, \"end\": 505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_McDonagh\", \"score\": 0.9999999999149622, \"rank\": 8.511736011955018e-11, \"text\": \"McDonagh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_McDonagh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_McDonagh\"}, {\"begin\": 560, \"end\": 567, \"title\": \